{"tid":34681,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"(自爆)敗家組合及心得","createTime":"2016-12-11T15:25:08.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-26T07:18:58.000Z","uid":62570,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"467171cfd2e7cbce3a1fcd783ba46eab57147227","tid":34681,"uid":62570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T15:25:08.000Z","msg":"小弟第一次開po，多多指教。<br />\n利申：唔係鼓吹買器材送技術...只係少少心得分享，希望新入坑的人洗少d冤枉錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，不喜勿插<br />\n<br />\nC記用家<br />\n6d(2012)<br />\nCanon 50 f1.8ii<br />\nCanon 24-70L f2.8ii<br />\nCanon 600Ex <br />\nCanon St-E3-rt <br />\nSigma 50 f1.4 art<br />\nCanon 85 f1.2 <br />\nCanon 70-200 f2.8ii <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Canon 50 f1.8ii</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tg05STh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTg05STh.jpg&h=2b1e6b3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新入坑第一支鏡強烈建議買支平50定焦(最平)，因為可以訓練一下用隻腳去構圖，kit鏡係方便，但好易令人懶。而且焦距同物距對壓縮感好大影響。真心想學影相，必購呢支窮人三寶<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Canon 24-70L f2.8ii</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/11/232034_2c11a8483cb564b589ff9b597a5c26d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F11%2F232034_2c11a8483cb564b589ff9b597a5c26d5.jpg&h=47a74d0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大三元之一，好重好貴，但焦距實用，成像好，日常生活大部分可應付，如果可以再揀，我都寧願買支f4就算，又平又輕，可惜已經返唔到轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Canon 600Ex &amp; St-E3-rt</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8vK2OmZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8vK2OmZ.jpg&h=e0ac79f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真心後悔入左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 除非你有強烈的原廠情誼結，否則大班副廠俾你玩，尤其當你玩到飛燈果陣，其實好易跌燈，而當你知道一支原廠等於三支副廠果陣，你個心會好似寸左個窿咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後再補其他，打左咁耐都係拋磚引各位討論一下，攝影係一個敗家的玩意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，器材唔一定必要，技術同埋創意先係先決。"},{"pid":"824ebbe2167a83adbd943561ab0122021d176da0","tid":34681,"uid":5335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T15:32:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4a439e2f3737c8821292aea1bdb18a17bda9cef7","tid":34681,"uid":36473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T16:08:58.000Z","msg":"Leica mp240<br />\n35/1.4 fle<br />\n一機一鏡走天涯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n2610C6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn2610C6.jpg&h=ab63d62d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"387fa331564b81125a05a343c47c701ab9605fad","tid":34681,"uid":62570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T16:39:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/11/233133_f5e50ec6e868403fa3b54945ba4cdebc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F11%2F233133_f5e50ec6e868403fa3b54945ba4cdebc.jpg&h=1f04e249&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nA7ii<br />\nSony fe28<br />\n輕 性價比高<br />\n已換sigma 24 art</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n支24 art好唔好用？<br />\n配Sony 對焦準唔準？<br />\n我部6d對焦簡直係想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c5d684ed232ad83b3c33da4d475b2d08cba44b9","tid":34681,"uid":2738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T16:57:07.000Z","msg":"碗麵有d壽包feel"},{"pid":"8250dccc5ae5ed6f9f22539b8a2c6a22ff4aee48","tid":34681,"uid":62570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T17:05:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>碗麵有d壽包feel</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n姐係點？"},{"pid":"1dd820b468e2bc2cd6cb9f735a18d8f8e3459284","tid":34681,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T17:44:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>碗麵有d壽包feel</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n姐係點？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔似。<br />\n<br />\n壽包係好似俾人落毒但仲以為好型果隻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n碗麵冇乜野丫，普通相。"},{"pid":"66231c4c2f8244ad82ee956685bffef50b6e52f4","tid":34681,"uid":3811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T01:28:33.000Z","msg":"樓主親身教大家與其花大錢買器材不如花時間練多啲影多啲"},{"pid":"5c20e11315a201b24f4dcc6875762815e6f63b24","tid":34681,"uid":12599,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T01:29:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主親身教大家與其花大錢買器材不如花時間練多啲影多啲</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0012a6f010e1b744a30e2d7cad11d02a15cc6796","tid":34681,"uid":62570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T02:30:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主親身教大家與其花大錢買器材不如花時間練多啲影多啲</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 放得上黎就唔好怕俾人批評"},{"pid":"a9d02fe7d4685d1f3ba315937f7f403f3047607d","tid":34681,"uid":40445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T02:35:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主親身教大家與其花大錢買器材不如花時間練多啲影多啲</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 放得上黎就唔好怕俾人批評</blockquote><br />\n好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a65f67b0876e8c78669fae6a98ebf826b1215b5","tid":34681,"uid":44458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T03:59:42.000Z","msg":"敗家同識影係兩樣野黎既"},{"pid":"664c9255b67f98e783ad159685313fea04453552","tid":34681,"uid":7119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T05:01:03.000Z","msg":"教學post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" 